{"_path":"/zh_hans/getting-started/assets","_dir":{"_path":"/zh_hans/getting-started/assets/_dir","title":"资源"},"_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"概述","description":"游戏的资源管理器","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在游戏内各种演出效果需要调用不同游戏资源以便使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"进行预加载资源后，在使用到该资源时可以立刻作用并呈现，否则会进行动态加载，直到加载完毕才显现正确效果（PC端游戏由于资源在本地，加载时间较快）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果用于移动端，则图片尺寸不应超过4096x4096"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"资源类别和支持的格式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"资源类别和支持的格式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"基础资源"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"【基础资源】"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"图片：png、jpg、jpeg"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文本：txt、json"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"音频：mp3、ogg"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"视频：mp4、webm"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"高级资源"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"【高级资源】"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高级资源由对应的制作数据以及多种基础资源组合而成"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「场景：Scene」 可能包含若干场景对象、图层引用的图片资源"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「场景对象：SceneObject」 可能包含行走图、若干挂载的动画和挂载的界面"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「行走图：Avatar」 可能包含图片、引用的部件（行走图）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「立绘：StandAvatar」 可能包含图片、引用的部件（立绘）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text